{
  "video_id": "7TYpKy-Gsw8",
  "title": "The case for universal basic income | Steven Shafarman | TEDxMidAtlantic",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Michele Gianella Reviewer: Ellen Maloney"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21340.0,
      "end_time": 23530.0,
      "text": "Basic income is in the news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23880.0,
      "end_time": 29400.0,
      "text": "often called UBI, Universal - or unconditional - Basic Income."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 30640.0,
      "end_time": 33360.0,
      "text": "Mark Zuckerberg and Elon Musk are promoting it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 34520.0,
      "end_time": 36920.0,
      "text": "Keith Ellison, vice chair of the Democratic Party,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 36920.0,
      "end_time": 38300.0,
      "text": "has endorsed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38230.0,
      "end_time": 40640.0,
      "text": "Hillary Clinton mentions it in her latest book."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42460.0,
      "end_time": 45760.0,
      "text": "Pilot projects are underway or about to begin"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46360.0,
      "end_time": 48400.0,
      "text": "in Oakland and Stockton, California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48860.0,
      "end_time": 55800.0,
      "text": "and underway in Finland, Holland, Canada and Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56160.0,
      "end_time": 59800.0,
      "text": "The idea is to set some amount, say $1,000 a month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 60520.0,
      "end_time": 62880.0,
      "text": "and provide that to every adult citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62880.0,
      "end_time": 64480.0,
      "text": "The same amount for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 65720.0,
      "end_time": 68720.0,
      "text": "Funds would come from cutting programs that become superfluous."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 74000.0,
      "end_time": 77280.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been a basic income activist for more than 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 77570.0,
      "end_time": 83800.0,
      "text": "And I find that this idea can attract, excite, and unite"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 83800.0,
      "end_time": 86399.0,
      "text": "Liberal Democrats and Conservative Republicans"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 86400.0,
      "end_time": 90800.0,
      "text": "and people who are normally apolitical or anti-political."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 91480.0,
      "end_time": 95800.0,
      "text": "We can end hunger, homelessness and extreme poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 97390.0,
      "text": "and make real rapid progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 97400.0,
      "end_time": 100640.0,
      "text": "on health care, education, immigration and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 101880.0,
      "end_time": 103420.0,
      "text": "Consider climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 104840.0,
      "end_time": 106800.0,
      "text": "Economists and environmentalists"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 106800.0,
      "end_time": 109160.0,
      "text": "and politicians from the left and the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 111200.0,
      "text": "endorse the idea of tax and dividend."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 111760.0,
      "end_time": 114400.0,
      "text": "This plan puts the dividend first"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 114680.0,
      "end_time": 117560.0,
      "text": "and will likely lead to a consensus on tax reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 120600.0,
      "end_time": 121919.0,
      "text": "This idea is not new."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 123550.0,
      "end_time": 126280.0,
      "text": "In fact, it goes back to the America&#39;s founders:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 127160.0,
      "end_time": 129639.0,
      "text": "Thomas Jefferson, Thomas Paine and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 130919.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133910.0,
      "text": "In order to truly secure our inalienable rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 133910.0,
      "end_time": 136680.0,
      "text": "to life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 136700.0,
      "end_time": 138579.0,
      "text": "basic income is imperative."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 140900.0,
      "end_time": 143520.0,
      "text": "Life requires food and shelter at least."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 143520.0,
      "end_time": 144960.0,
      "text": "Without an income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 144960.0,
      "end_time": 147800.0,
      "text": "liberty is precarious and happiness elusive."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 148560.0,
      "end_time": 152440.0,
      "text": "A majority of Americans supported related ideas in the 1960s."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 152440.0,
      "end_time": 154160.0,
      "text": "The House of Representatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 154160.0,
      "end_time": 158760.0,
      "text": "passed a bill to provide a guaranteed income for families"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 158760.0,
      "end_time": 160000.0,
      "text": "by a vote of two to one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160680.0,
      "end_time": 162420.0,
      "text": "but the Senate then blocked it."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 163360.0,
      "end_time": 165720.0,
      "text": "Alaskans already have a small basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 165720.0,
      "end_time": 167290.0,
      "text": "the Permanent Fund dividend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 172590.0,
      "text": "and I recently met with a state senator from Alaska"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 173640.0,
      "end_time": 175760.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s looking at ways to expand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 176840.0,
      "end_time": 178520.0,
      "text": "Hawaii now has a law"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 178520.0,
      "end_time": 183800.0,
      "text": "declaring that every family is entitled to financial security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 183800.0,
      "end_time": 186680.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve launched a task force for basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 191280.0,
      "end_time": 194280.0,
      "text": "One of the proponents in the 1960s was Martin Luther King."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 195630.0,
      "end_time": 198000.0,
      "text": "He had a dream, and we can make it come true."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 199240.0,
      "end_time": 202680.0,
      "text": "I believe that we can have a peaceful democratic revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 202680.0,
      "end_time": 204400.0,
      "text": "within the next three to five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 205800.0,
      "end_time": 206800.0,
      "text": "You can play a leading role."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 207840.0,
      "end_time": 209100.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s make history."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 209560.0,
      "end_time": 210780.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 210780.0,
      "end_time": 212330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}